      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\" \u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eDemand Forecasting App\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n      This app forecasts product demand across multiple stores using historical sales data. It combines exploratory analysis, time-series decomposition, feature engineering, and machine learning (LightGBM) to predict sales for the next 3 months with high accuracy.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) reports: dataset shape, unique values, missing values, date ranges, and descriptive statistics\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Business insights: average sales by store, item, and store-item pairs; highest and most consistent sales combinations\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Feature engineered dataset including lag features, rolling means, exponentially weighted means, one-hot encoding, and date features\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Time-series decomposition plots highlighting trend, seasonality, and residuals\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eKey Highlights\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cb\u003eModel:\u003c/b\u003e LightGBM for scalable and accurate sales forecasting\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cb\u003eTime-Series Features\u003c/b\u003e\r\n        \u003c!---ul\u003e\r\n          \u003cli\u003eLag features to capture past performance\u003c/li\u003e\r\n          \u003cli\u003eRolling mean \u0026amp; standard deviation for trend smoothing\u003c/li\u003e\r\n          \u003cli\u003eExponentially weighted moving averages for recent sensitivity\u003c/li\u003e\r\n          \u003cli\u003eDate-based features (month, weekday, quarter, year, etc.)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003c/ul---\u003e\r\n      \u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cb\u003eFlexibility:\u003c/b\u003e Execution flow adapts based on input parameters \u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cb\u003eEvaluation:\u003c/b\u003e Uses SMAPE (Symmetric Mean Absolute Percentage Error) to measure forecasting accuracy\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n",
